<span id="freeTextContainer11773624499751731760">As the world descends into crisis, people are searching for alternatives to our current social system. In the framework of a revised Marxism, this book shows how a more cooperative and democratic economy is already emerging, and how we can build on its successes. Society may be on the cusp of the greatest revolutionary movement in history.</span>

